author: doll
msg: The dataservice json rest code now allows the special tokens @viewer, @owner and @app. These get translated behind the service layer so that containers can make optimizations based on the token.
This involved adding a new UserId class and pulling the GroupId class to the top level. GroupId now supports arbitrary groups. Changed all interfaces to take the UserId and added tests.
